review_title: Horrific app, customer service also not on top
review_description: About a month ago they withdrew the service amount without any problem, however, on the next day they charged the same amount saying that the first transaction was not successful. Obviously I had to e-mail them and keep calling my bank for the next 3 weeks to get this amount back. Furthermore, the app itself didn't work when I wanted to take pictures at the beginning / closing of the rental at least a dozen times and since you cannot take pictures at the beginning you can't use the car. There shouldn't even be a price plan if the app is unusable.

The cars are great, all electrical, perfect for the city.
The prices are fair, the best ones in Budapest for similar services. 
Sometimes it is a bit long to open the car, but still acceptable.
The customer service is of high standard! Far better than the one of the competition. That clearly is a differentiator and makes it my favorite option.

A super community car-sharing business with helpful customer service! To live a sustainable urban life, it is essential to reduce the use of private cars, if possible even sell your car (or don't buy one in the first place!).
